text: I think Anna is great! Going into this, I just wanted to have my palm read for the experience to say that I have done it. Anna helps you see not only what’s going on around you, but within yourself. I highly recommend her and giving it a shot.

name: Amanda Daniel
text: I’ve had several tarot reading done by different people and I can easily say that, hands down, this was the best, most accurate and detailed reading I have ever had! First of all, Anna was kind enough to stay and read for me even though I was fairly late arriving. She was very attentive to my question and concern and gave me a lot of insight about the issue at hand but also was able to pick up on numerous other energies and transits currently taking place in my life. I was absolutely astonished at how many specific details she was able to point out and offer insight about. For example, several details that i had not even included in my questions were addressed. I can’t wait to go back!

name: Alyssa Lauren
text: Anna is absolutely amazing! Her readings are spot on and she is so caring! I have been seeing her for 8 months now and she has been phenomenal and helped me through so much. You will not go wrong by allowing Anna to lead you in the right direction. She is a Godly woman who will always put God first. Thank you Anna for all you do.

name: Melanie Zinn
text:
Nothing I didn't already know. Didn't really tell me my future at all and the one REALLY important question I needed answered more than anything, she couldn't answer. I believe she got my children and past relationships mixed up in the reading and it was just all jumbled around.

I was so excited to go because of all her great reviews, but I got absolutely no closure and honestly no "future reading" basically a reading telling me what's going on currently (which I'm aware of and living, so no help there). Drove over an hour. Just very disappointed. Really hoped to get some clear answers. She was very sweet, so I will give her that, but as far as getting anything from the reading....I pulled over in tears because nothing was answered and just disappointed. I got no closure.
